summary: hbo is really out here making jon and dany fan videos! i kid. we have the night king as well as an appearance or two from bran...
caption:
hbo is really out here making jon and dany fan videos!

i kid. we have the night king as well as an appearance or two from bran (bran is paralleled/or melded with the night king in terms of the visual imagery so, make of that what you will). 

but the majority of the video is jon and dany, and their heroes’ journeys that have led them to this moment and that make them westeros’ hope.

they couldn’t be any more obvious about where this is going. but i guess some people gonna keep being trifling.

summary: Oh, my sweet summer child, what do you know about fear? Fear is for the winter, when the shows fall a hundred feet deep. Fear is...
body:
Oh, my sweet summer child, what do you know about fear? Fear is for the winter, when the shows fall a hundred feet deep. Fear is for the Long Night, when the sun hides for years. And children are born and live and die, all in darkness. That is the time for fear, my little lord, when the White Walkers moves through the woods. Thousands of years ago, there came a night that lasted a generation. Kings froze to death in their castles, same as the shepherds in their huts. And women smother their babies, rather than see them starve, and wept and felt the tears freeze on their cheeks. In that Darkness, the White Walkers came of for the first time. They swept through cities and kingdoms, riding their dead horses, hunting with their packs of pale spiders, big as hounds.

Old Nan, Game of Thrones
